      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and ASME V&V 10 were used to verify the FEA solver for large-deformation elasto-plastic beam bending. All benchmark results within 1% of analytical solutions. Required and achieved level both 2."
