      "rationale": "Mesh convergence study performed with four successive refinements (h-refinement) on the pedicle screw shank and rod interface regions. Richardson extrapolation applied; GCI < 2% for all QoIs on the production mesh. Required level 3; achieved level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
