      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Nonlinear solver residual convergence criteria set to 1e-6 relative norm. Iterative solution monitored for all load steps; no divergence events observed across 11 model instances. Required and achieved level both 2."
