      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Continuum elasto-plastic model with isotropic hardening used for Ti-6Al-4V screw and cobalt-chrome rod. Contact modeled with augmented Lagrangian formulation. Model form consistent with published literature for metallic implant constructs under quasi-static bending. Required and achieved level both 3."
    },
    {
