      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Material properties (E, yield stress, tangent modulus) sourced from coupon testing of production-lot material. Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of the actual test constructs. Friction coefficients from published tribology data for Ti-6Al-4V on CoCr. Parametric uncertainty bounds established for all inputs. Required and achieved level both 3."
    },
    {
