      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH OSEL and DePuy Synthes R&D). All constructs from production lots with documented traceability. Sample size exceeds minimum for statistical comparison per ASTM E2935. Required level 3; achieved level 4."
    },
    {
