      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single loading condition (quasi-static compression-bending per ASTM F1717 at 10 mm/min). Only one test condition evaluated; no variation in loading rate or temperature. This factor is below the required level, representing the known gap identified in the COU description. Required level 3; achieved level 2."
    },
